g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de72b26a82494cd3083c428156adf9fb3d3ae0f7","tid":290142,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想睇kobe 夾bosh love 會唔會整廢佢地</blockquote><br />\nkobe整廢過邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上冇一個係走左之後反而勁左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左ariza<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n猴活囉 第一中鋒冇波到變到傻仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n猴活走左之後反而勁左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n你話kobe整廢過邊個ma<br />\n我咪答你猴活囉<br />\n冇話佢走左之後勁左</blockquote><br />\n太多傷啦佢，同埋我覺得佢本身實力係去到呢到</blockquote><br />\n連續三四年穩坐第一中鋒個位<br />\n都算勁架啦 係去湖人冇波到之後廢左七成<br />\n再之後就冇晒鬥志打了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身有傷未好哂<br />\n季尾kobe叫佢照打都唔制"},{"pid":"b7c4512aaecf7cf4c179141c990b9c2ab72a801c","tid":290142,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T19:46:50.000Z","msg":"咪撚拎啲靠身體質素強行殺籃 簽隊友 抱團狗同高比 佢永遠都唔配<br />\n數據上好有撚用<br />\n影響力 可觀性 霸氣全部都輸高比<br />\n係啲傻仔跟條25仔轉隊 又熱火又騎士<br />\n諗定之後買咩波衫啦"}]}